info.description: ## This is the main folder for organizing all Car Rental API collections, including endpoints for car management, health checks, authentication, and user management

tags.name: Cars
tags.description:
### Endpoints for managing car data, available only to authorized users with specific roles.

### Note :

- base_url = localhost:3000/api/v1
    
- token = your jwt token.
